dataset.title: Two new species of the genus Panau (Lepidoptera: Cossidae) from the Philippines and Indonesia, with the redescription of Panau variegatum

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Yakovlev, R. V., Hulsbosch, R. (2023): Two new species of the genus Panau (Lepidoptera: Cossidae) from the Philippines and Indonesia, with the redescription of Panau variegatum. Zoosystematica Rossica (Zoosyst. Rossica) 32 (1): 3-7, DOI: 10.31610/zsr/2023.32.1.3, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.31610/zsr/2023.32.1.3
